# --- Memory Machine Exclusions ---

# Ignore heavy 3D model files (too big for GitHub)
*.3dm
*.3mb
*.gh
*.ghx

# Ignore temporary Rhino/Grasshopper backup files
*.tmp
*.bak
*.autosave
*.~*

# Ignore System & IDE junk
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/

# --- Keep These (Safety Check) ---
!data/*.csv
!data/*.json
!logic/*.py
!*.html
!archive/render_output/*

# --- Explicitly Protect Precedent & Render Files ---
!*bottega_louie*
!*ot_johnson*
!*bottegaLouie*
!*BottegaLouie*
!*OTjohnson*
!*OTJohnson*
!precedents/
!render_outputs/

# --- Explicitly Protect All Render Image Formats ---
!*.png
!*.jpg
!*.jpeg